basic.blooming: Flowering period April-May, fruiting period July to September
basic.color: Leaf color green , fruit color light brown

maintenance.soil: Likes sandy loam or well-drained slightly acidic soil
maintenance.sunlight: Like sunshine, slightly resistant to half shade
maintenance.watering: Water thoroughly after soil surface dries, avoid saturated water
maintenance.fertilization: Dilute fertilizers following instructions, apply 1-2 times monthly
maintenance.pruning: Remove aged tissues, dead and pest branches timely
